name: Angō-ka sa reta pōtoforio 暗号化されたポートフォリオ
description:
Crypto-portfolio[or meta-portfolio] are works of art that utilize the form of the book(pdf, in blockchains). They are often published in small editions, though they are sometimes produced as one-of-a-kind objects.
Subscribe @wasem_simon twitter account for full quality pdf, with link of transaction.
